yingyinNormal.en: Ah, but that's, I mean, it's impossible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，但是，这不可能。

yingyinNormal.en: It's Letty, isn't it? It's impossible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是莱蒂，对吗？这不可能。

yingyinNormal.en: It's impossible. Why? Two people can't have identical DNA.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是不可能的。怎么了？两个人的DNA不可能完全相同。

yingyinNormal.en: We're gonna need it back. Impossible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们要把东西拿回来。这决不可能。

yingyinNormal.en: Money! Yes! That's, that's, that's impossible!
yingyinNormal.zh: 钱！没错！这，这，这不可能！
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge Out of Water》

yingyinNormal.en: I'm sorry. I'm sorry. This thing's impossible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对不起，对不起，这东西不可能拼出来的。

yingyinNormal.en: Man made a world where standing together is impossible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 人类是不可能“同心协力”的。

yingyinNormal.en: Of course, this is impossible, not to mention illegal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然，这是不可能的，何况还违法。

yingyinNormal.en: It's not impossible, merely un-possible. Got ya!
yingyinNormal.zh: 问题不是不可能，而是我们无法实现。抓到了！跑了！
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《爱丽丝梦游仙境2：镜中奇遇记》

yingyinNormal.en: Reverse the ray? That's brilliant. But, it's impossible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 扭转射线？这太机智了！但是，这不可能！

yingyinNormal.en: Thank you, that's the end of my amazingly impossible circus.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢，我的神奇的不可能的马戏团表演要结束了。

yingyinNormal.en: Magellan? You got 46 states. What? That's impossible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 麦哲伦先生？你只答对了46个州，什么？ 那是不可能的。

yingyinNormal.en: So, why attempt the impossible? Why follow your dream?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那为何要挑战不可能？为何要追寻梦想？

yingyinNormal.en: What's impossible, Troy? I wouldn't think impossible is even in your vocabulary.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么事不可能，特洛伊？我认为你的字典里没有"不可能"三个字。

yingyinNormal.en: I have had a vision. Tai Lung will return. That is impossible! He is in prison. Nothing is impossible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我有预感，太狼会重现江湖。不可能，他还在牢里。没什么不可能。

yingyinNormal.en: It's impossible. This bike is too noisy. I can't hear the TV.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不可能.这自行车太吵了。我听不到电视。

yingyinNormal.en: It's impossible. This bike is too noisy. I can't hear the TV.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不可能，这自行车太吵了。我听不到电视。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, that's impossible. Can you check again, please. Check again, please.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是不可能的，请再查一次。请再查一次。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh my God Phoebe, this is impossible. We can't do this by Friday. We have to find a place. We have to invite people. We have to get food.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不可能，我们不可能在星期五办，要找到一个地点，邀请客人，买好食物。

yingyinNormal.en: You said it yourself, it's the only way. That doesn't sound impossible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你自己说的，这是唯一的办法，这也不是不可能啊。
